Subject: [PATCH] mtd: slram: insert break after errors in parsing the map
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 336c218dd7f0588ed8a7345f367975a00a4f003f
